{"tid":1512995,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］想去送札花比嘉道理後人","createTime":"2019-08-28T06:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T00:53:15.000Z","uid":8687,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"425ebf048d32a8c92808caab5386911520b50ad2","tid":1512995,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:33:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2461856810712350&amp;id=1551349795096394\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2461856810712350%26id%3D1551349795096394&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ5a0YVntLK4LebkCjpCDSOM%3D&h=9d309c4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2461856810712350&amp;id=1551349795096394</a><br />\n<br />\nSam：米高．嘉道理爵士喺南華早報登廣告，希望政府唔好再搞香港。<br />\n<br />\n大意：香港係將中國駁通世界嘅橋樑。拆走呢條橋，中國同香港就攬炒。<br />\n<br />\nA Letter to the People of Hong Kong<br />\n《致香港人書》<br />\n<br />\nThe Kadoories first arrived in Hong Kong 140 years ago and this city gave us the opportunity to prosper. 嘉道理家喺 140 年前初到貴境。當年嘅香港扶植我家嘅生意發展。<br />\n<br />\nOver the past century we have been welcomed by the Chinese people and have been privileged to play a small part in Hong Kong&rsquo;s transformation from a bustling port to a dynamic metropolis on the world stage. 咁耐以嚟，由初初嘅港口，到今日繁華嘅大都會，華人唔單止無嫌棄過我哋，仲畀機會我哋喺香港發展期間，出一分力。<br />\n<br />\nMy late father often spoke about the uniqueness of Hong Kong. 先父經常都提到香港嘅獨一無二之處。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;This area of the world,&rdquo; he once said, &ldquo;is going to develop as a neutral point of contact between two different ideologists and two different systems of government.&rdquo; 佢話：「呢個地方，將會發展成一個『中立點』，連繫住兩套意式形態同兩種政治制度。」<br />\n<br />\nThis prediction made more than three decades ago is evident in the city&rsquo;s prosperity and growth, intrinsically linked to China&rsquo;s economic development. 從今日香港嘅發展，我哋可以睇得出，佢當年嘅預測係啱嘅。香港嘅繁榮同中國嘅經濟，係唇齒相依嘅。<br />\n<br />\nWith this deep connection, it is disheartening to see what has overtaken the city recently with the threat of a challenging situation escalating still further. 既然兩者嘅連繫係咁密切，所以睇住香港作為「中立點」嘅地位日益受到破壞，係令人痛心疾首嘅。<br />\n<br />\nI do not support violence nor do I believe that this should be the way to resolve conflicts. 我唔支持暴力，我亦都唔認為暴力係解決問題嘅方法。<br />\n<br />\nA commitment to the rule of law and maintaining peace and order is the cornerstone of Hong Kong&rsquo;s success. 法治同治安係香港賴以成功嘅基石。<br />\n<br />\nMore importantly, our city&rsquo;s spirit that we have long valued is our ability to find solutions in mutual respect, understanding and open dialogue. 更重要嘅係，香港人係講道理嘅。有咩唔啱，咪大家坐低四四六六拆掂佢囉。<br />\n<br />\nWe must not forget our unique place as that neutral point of contact and work tirelessly to restore the balance. 我哋千萬不能忘記，香港係一個（將中國同世界連接嘅）「中立點」 。我哋無論如何，都要回復呢個原貌。<br />\n<br />\nI have spoken many times of how how our young people are Hong Kong&rsquo;s future. 我多次強調，年輕人係香港嘅未來。<br />\n<br />\nWe cannot leave them in desperation or despair. 我哋唔可以迫佢哋上絕路。<br />\n<br />\nIt is the responsibility of us all to rebuild trust in the community and create hope for the younger generation. 我哋嘅責任，係要令到年輕人見到前路，令個社會有返信任。<br />\n<br />\nBeing a part of Hong Kong has instilled the Lion Rock Spirit in me and my children &mdash; 作為香港嘅一份子，獅子山精神一直都喺我同我小朋友嘅身體流動。<br />\n<br />\nthat energy, ambition, drive and creativity has powered our prosperity and helped us to face many challenges. 獅子山精神令我哋百戰百勝。<br />\n<br />\nMy faith in our home is undiminished. 我對香港好有信心。<br />\n<br />\nNow is a time for everybody to unite and be unswerving in our commitment not just to Hong Kong&rsquo;s special place, but to a peaceful solution to our current crisis for this generation, the next, and beyond. 而家要萬眾一心，解決當前危機、認清香港嘅特殊地位係不能動搖，為後世建立一個美好嘅香港。<br />\n<br />\n簡而清說明 [中立] 先係香港成功之道<br />\n就係呢廿幾年不斷有人迫你企邊<br />\n不繼對香港毛手毛腳<br />\n有班人明知比人毛手毛腳都唔 say no 仲故意迎合<br />\n<br />\n我地要光復香港中立地位<br />\n將呢廿幾年故意迎合既仆街趕走！！<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知嘉道理後人而家住邊？"},{"pid":"d237d9152cc54c3ec5a4481c073fda40a